---
import LandingLayout from '../layouts/LandingLayout.astro'
import Header from '../components/landing/Header.astro'
import Footer from '../components/landing/Footer.astro'
---

<LandingLayout
  title="Privacy Policy - Chat2Note"
  description="Privacy policy for Chat2Note browser extension - learn how we protect your data and ensure complete privacy."
>
  <Header />
  <main class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-950">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16 max-w-4xl">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-8">Last updated: October 4, 2025</p>

      <div class="prose prose-lg dark:prose-invert max-w-none">
        <section class="mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">Introduction</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
            Chat2Note is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how our browser extension handles your data with a privacy-first approach.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">Data Collection and Processing</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
            <strong class="text-gray-900 dark:text-white">We do not collect, transmit, or store any of your personal data on external servers.</strong>
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
            All data processing happens entirely locally in your browser:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 space-y-2 mb-4">
            <li>Conversation extraction occurs directly in your browser tabs</li>
            <li>Export operations are processed locally without any external transmission</li>
            <li>Configuration settings are stored only in your browser's local storage</li>
            <li>No analytics, tracking, or telemetry data is collected</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">Third-Party Services</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
            When you choose to export conversations to third-party services (such as Notion or Obsidian):
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 space-y-2 mb-4">
            <li><strong class="text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Notion:</strong> API tokens you provide are encrypted and stored locally in your browser. Exported data is sent directly from your browser to Notion's API without passing through our servers.</li>
            <li><strong class="text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Obsidian:</strong> Data is transferred directly to your local Obsidian vault using the Obsidian URI scheme, entirely on your device.</li>
            <li><strong class="text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Local Files:</strong> Files are downloaded directly to your device without any external transmission.</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
            These third-party services have their own privacy policies, which we encourage you to review.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">Permissions</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
            Chat2Note requests the following browser permissions:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 space-y-2 mb-4">
            <li><strong class="text-gray-900 dark:text-white">activeTab:</strong> To access and extract content from AI chat platform pages you're currently viewing</li>
            <li><strong class="text-gray-900 dark:text-white">storage:</strong> To save your preferences and configuration locally in your browser</li>
            <li><strong class="text-gray-900 dark:text-white">downloads:</strong> To save exported files to your device</li>
            <li><strong class="text-gray-900 dark:text-white">clipboardWrite:</strong> To copy exported content to your clipboard</li>
            <li><strong class="text-gray-900 dark:text-white">contextMenus:</strong> To provide right-click export functionality</li>
            <li><strong class="text-gray-900 dark:text-white">scripting:</strong> To inject export functionality into supported chat platforms</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
            These permissions are used exclusively for the extension's core functionality and never for data collection.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">Data Security</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
            We implement security best practices to protect your data:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 space-y-2 mb-4">
            <li>API tokens (such as Notion tokens) are encrypted using industry-standard encryption before being stored locally</li>
            <li>All data processing occurs in isolated browser contexts</li>
            <li>No data is transmitted to external servers operated by Chat2Note</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">Updates to This Policy</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
            We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify users of any material changes by updating the "Last updated" date at the top of this policy. Continued use of Chat2Note after changes constitutes acceptance of the updated policy.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">Contact</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
            If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at <a href="mailto:support@chat2note.com" class="text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-700 dark:text-primary-400 dark:hover:text-primary-300 underline">support@chat2note.com</a>.
          </p>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</LandingLayout>
